00:03:47.955 --> 00:03:48.830
JON PETERSON: Swiped.

00:03:48.830 --> 00:03:49.860
KYLE NEWMAN: --some of the--

00:03:49.860 --> 00:03:50.660
JON PETERSON: Yeah.

00:03:50.660 --> 00:03:53.118
KYLE NEWMAN: --some of the key
