00:49:17.740 --> 00:49:19.840
Ken Kelly was the same
guy who did "Love Gun."

00:49:19.840 --> 00:49:22.120
The "Love Gun" cover for Kiss.

00:49:22.120 --> 00:49:24.880
So these things really were
kind of the same community

00:49:24.880 --> 00:49:27.430
of people that were involved
in it, who were doing the art.

00:49:27.430 --> 00:49:29.020
They were creating the visuals.

00:49:29.020 --> 00:49:30.120
And they all kind
of went together.

00:49:30.120 --> 00:49:31.703
KYLE NEWMAN: But it
