00:51:31.150 --> 00:51:32.120
of its different eras--

00:51:32.120 --> 00:51:33.370
MICHAEL WITWER: Which edition?

00:51:33.370 --> 00:51:34.210
Or which piece of art?

00:51:34.210 --> 00:51:34.690
I'm sorry.

