time whimsy and humor.

00:53:09.070 --> 00:53:10.720
The main player
characters always

00:53:10.720 --> 00:53:12.450
looked like a bunch of wackos.

00:53:12.450 --> 00:53:13.924
Just really weird.

00:53:13.924 --> 00:53:16.090
If you look in the book and
see any of Erol's stuff,

00:53:16.090 --> 00:53:18.291
